commit be016d3c9fbee69f7b1c31edd868670d9cb68cc8
Author: Clifford Yapp <238416+starseeker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Mon Jul 15 11:58:25 2024 -0400

    Add previous facetize logic back in as facetize_old
    
    Because the new facetize system is such a radical departure from older
    codes, add the 7.38.2 facetize logic to have as a backup under the
    command name facetize_old.  This can go away as we get more confidence
    in the new setup, so it's not being announced as a command per-say, but
    it will be available to try if the new logic isn't working for some
    reason.

