commit 57c27a39d2fc4649f3a56f1ec5dcca605f83ec33
Author: Clifford Yapp <238416+starseeker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Thu Jul 11 17:17:56 2024 -0400

    Fail early and hard if we can't process a region.

commit 71f33e4f1b77566ed90b18328b181658d1a20729
Author: Clifford Yapp <238416+starseeker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Thu Jul 11 15:59:58 2024 -0400

    Optimize how we process per-region facetizations
    
    We were treating each region like a complete conversion, but we don't
    want to do that - it's inefficient and launches too many subprocesses.
    Instead, handle all the solids up front and then handle just the boolean
    evaluations individually.

commit 29134ef5e2c487b1e027a778f7d4c4569d3009ea
Author: Clifford Yapp <238416+starseeker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Thu Jul 11 14:05:48 2024 -0400

    Allow for disabling the bext library staging
    
    In situations where the LIEF rpath management isn't working, the
    BRLCAD_DISABLE_RELOCATION variable can be enabled to disable the bext
    setup process.  This will make it the responsibility of the developer to
    set all necessary variables on the configure line so BRL-CAD can find
    the necessary components for building.

