commit 81ef42b4fd6fd1684379538590b2d288b341a61e
Author: f4alt <christopherjmacgregor@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Jun 17 16:19:26 2024 -0400

    GetUserNameEx is not part of standard Windows API
    
    Ex is only part of the Windows security API which is not linked with
    WinBase. Including it would only gain slightly improved username
    formatting - which we're not utilizing anyhow. Instead, let's only use
    the base supplied GetUserName function.

