commit fcf61e4109babee3a246f9aff9e6777aee15da00
Author: Clifford Yapp <238416+starseeker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Wed Jun 12 15:15:55 2024 -0400

    Get all the BoT lint tests working in parallel
    
    Most of the logic is common between these tests, so refactor to take
    advantage of that fact.
    
    When running in a parallel bu_log is wiping out MGED, even on Linux, so
    temporarily quell the hooks.

commit ef937e217217902cd5cbcd381c0d9ea40b787c47
Author: Clifford Yapp <238416+starseeker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Wed Jun 12 10:05:22 2024 -0400

    Failure was on the CI end - revert lint backout
    
    Chris McGregor found it - apparently a misconfigured Windows image was
    used for the github runners.  See the following issue for more info:
    https://github.com/actions/runner-images/issues/10004
    
    Reverts commit 76e46aa9b3d1c136d8c1e6891c73e229ca025e25.

