commit 852653c355cc46f50030766f67c21afa92451d94
Author: Clifford Yapp <238416+starseeker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Tue May 28 10:28:30 2024 -0400

    Revert "Rename function - more to this than just thinness"
    
    This reverts commit ae4e26626f0adda3bfd1f9f9945b77afdf26a1c9.
    
    I think we're going to want to split this into two functions - the "thin"
    volumes we want to process, the "close above" case we just need to warn about
    since it's much harder to fix.

commit a3e80727663b0c2e6eb54cf1595ee6559e445810
