commit dd22e15e56527d6b396b0e19adef5a1896b0390b
Author: f4alt <christopherjmacgregor@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed May 15 16:24:45 2024 -0400

    openInGUI needs some tlc
    
    using this commit more as a means of documenting a TODO. current
    width/length settings for the popup make the window HUGE, not indicative
    of the actual report, and is not resizable.
    
    Also, throws an ugly NULL pointer error when destroying the window.

