commit 12861c742faf91f1aef6ae860213a53e64d772f1
Author: Clifford Yapp <238416+starseeker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Wed May 22 21:13:17 2024 -0400

    Adjust bot repair to accept multiple inputs
    
    The most common use case for this is most likely going to be "I have a
    .g file, fix all the BoTs in it."  Update the usability of the bot
    repair command accordingly - now "bot repair *" will try to repair all
    the BoT solids in a database.  For the case where a user wants to write
    the repair of a single bot to an object name, the -o option is now
    available rather than using an optional second argument.

