commit f67ae96926c2efbb85804f43626754cd0d70808b
Merge: e7e7947b36 b21128bfcb
Author: Clifford Yapp <238416+starseeker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Wed May 15 10:50:48 2024 -0400

    Merge new facetize work into main
    
    distcheck-full is now passing - merge the facetize branch back into
    main.  This work improves the conversion success rate of facetize in BoT
    mode significantly - although the process is slow, on Linux we have
    successfully run conversion.sh --bot MAXTIME=5000 against all of the .g
    example files in share/db and the share/db/* subfolders.
    
    Need to do more usability cleanup - improve user messages, make sure
    documentation is up to date, etc. - but things seem to be doing well
    enough now that we can avoid the overhead of working in a branch while
    tying up the lose ends.

