commit 0d77d4ed7f6bab6f7704499ae7c7aa38559ea3ba
Author: Clifford Yapp <238416+starseeker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Tue May 7 20:18:14 2024 -0400

    Update libged drawing tests that use facetization
    
    The new facetize setup results in slightly different triangles being
    produced for moss geometries, which in turn means the images are
    slightly different.  Output names of subtree objects are also different,
    so update select callouts accordingly.
    
    To really do this right these tests should set up caches local to the
    build directory so multiple builds can't interfere with facetize
    outputs - TODO notes added.

