commit 5d4fd080688ae5d2c172eeed0703804567d53840
Author: Clifford Yapp <238416+starseeker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Thu Mar 21 12:16:44 2024 -0400

    Remove db5_standardize_avs calls, add attr standardize
    
    The db5_standardize_avs process proved to be too expensive to run every
    time we are reading and writing a comb.  Instead, add a "standardize"
    subcommand to the attr command to allow the user to trigger the process
    manually.

